            <!-- SYSTEM DESIGN OVERVIEW -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">System Design</div>
                
                <p>This section demonstrates how the Calloway Pharmacy IMS processes system functionality to automate pharmacy operations and return processed results to users. The system design illustrates how various user levels interact and transact with the system, ensuring efficient management of inventory, sales, and customer data. The overall architecture of the website system is represented through comprehensive procedures and structured interactions shown in Figure 3.</p>

                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h4>üéØ System Design Objectives</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Automate critical pharmacy operations (POS, inventory, ordering)</li>
                        <li>Provide seamless user interaction through intuitive interfaces</li>
                        <li>Ensure data consistency and integrity across all modules</li>
                        <li>Enable real-time reporting and decision-making</li>
                        <li>Maintain secure and efficient transaction processing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="diagram-container">
                    <h3 style="color: #17a2b8; margin-bottom: 30px;">Figure 3: System Design Architecture</h3>
                    
                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="user-box">üë• Customers</div>
                        <div class="arrow">‚Üì</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="design-box">üè™ Point of Sale (POS) Module</div>
                        <div class="arrow">‚Üì</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="design-box">üì¶ Inventory Management</div>
                        <div class="design-box" style="margin-left: 15px; margin-top: 0;">üîç Medicine Locator</div>
                        <div class="design-box" style="margin-left: 15px; margin-top: 0;">üõí Online Ordering</div>
                        <div class="arrow">‚Üì</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="design-box">üéüÔ∏è Loyalty QR System</div>
                        <div class="arrow">‚Üì</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="design-box">üìä Reports & Analytics</div>
                        <div class="arrow">‚Üì</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
                        <div class="database-box">üóÑÔ∏è Pharmacy Database<br>(MySQL/MariaDB)</div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
                        <div class="legend">
